  "paper_analysis": {
    "summary": "This paper presents https://2DMat.ChemDX.org, a web-based experimental data platform and database for 2D materials spanning synthesis and characterization, with an emphasis on RHEED growth monitoring and PL/Raman mapping. The platform standardizes upload, parsing, visualization, and sharing of raw experimental files, and adds ML toolkits for RHEED growth analysis and PL/Raman super-resolution; the main scientific contribution is the creation of a curated experimental 2D materials database and analysis workflow rather than a new material discovery.",
